# AUTH ENDPOINTS
####################

### Signup
# @name signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
"user"
    "password": "password123"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Check Auth (Get Me)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/check

### Logout
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout


